modName: Witcher 3 Yennefer and Triss ECE Presets
summary: These are just  ECE presets for characters based on Triss and Yennefer from the Witcher 3, they are useless without the mods below and their respective requirements.
descriptionHtml:
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35267/?]
[/url]These are just  ECE presets for characters based on Triss and Yennefer from the Witcher 3, they are useless without the mods below and their respective requirements.

[b]MODS REQUIRED
[/b]
Enhanced Character Edit  [color=#ffffff]no cheek fix, 2x sliders
[/color][color=#ffffff]ECEE - RANs Enhanced Character Edit Enhancer
KS HAIRDOS
BROWS
SG FEMALE TEXTURES
SG EYEBROWS
[/color]THE EYES OF BEAUTY
CBBE

Yennefer's hair is called Hide. Triss' hair is called Sky155

To insall just extract and drop the .slot files in your CME_save folder. 2 is Triss, 3 is Yen.

[b]SCREENSHOT MODS[/b]

WITCHER 3 FEMALE ARMORS
APACHII DIVINE ELEGANCE STORE
PRETTY SIT IDLES
NEW ANIMATION FOR MAGIC CASTING

If someone more capable than me could actually make followers it would be appreciated.

[b]
CREDITS
[/b]Bethesda, CD projekt Red, all the authors of the mods used.




Peace.
